<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>食谱；秘诀：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Can you tell us your <strong>recipe for</strong> happiness and a long life?
您能告诉我们您快乐和长寿的秘诀吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Living every day to the full, definitely.
